<br>
My little summary:<br>
<br>
Clerics:<br>
Great heals, restore experience upon death, good raw HP/AC buffers, can wear almost all armor types, lull, good factions, very popular in groups.<br>
<br>
Shamans:<br>
Can heal, fantastic all-around buffs for almost everything, can wear many armors, great debuffs (slows and resistance reducing kick ass), good DOT spells, have secondary attack, can summon pets, SOW...<br>
<br>
This is just a basic summary, each class has a lot more then listed here. However, it's a decent basis in picking what you want to do.<br>
<br>
-Gloobonious, Ogre Shaman of Rallos Zak.<br>
